{"tid":2093044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<請注意>7月10日起, 由香港入境英格蘭毋須隔離","createTime":"2020-07-03T14:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T15:21:33.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8dc7517a1e0a7d7d2e0351d50f8edb92df9ad94","tid":2093044,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200703&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=61124392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200703%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D61124392&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=9530dba4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200703%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D61124392&h=15fe8727\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200703&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=61124392</a><br />\n英國公佈「旅遊走廊」名單，取消名單上60個國家的隔離要求。由7月10日起，在名單上的國家或地區入境的旅客毋須接受14天隔離，香港、澳門、台灣、日本及南韓也在名單上，其餘國家包括希臘、西班牙及比利時等。目前大部份入境英國的旅客都要接受兩周隔離，但蘇格蘭及威爾斯仍未決定放寬旅遊限制。"},{"pid":"0bd9ea715ab4601893e5ba99b1649c80e258f718","tid":2093044,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c73b0953dab664f0514d588ee40b40a74cb19fc","tid":2093044,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca655a104dae2d22e10298e3178291630de7e12","tid":2093044,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"移民潮黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003639494355c11ebc4347f0ae5f449611ec1862","tid":2093044,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\